PrecisDirection to the Canadian International Trade Tribunal to (a) forthwith inquire into the matter of the importation of dairy product blends outside the coverage of Canada's tariff-rate quotas, and (b) hold public hearings with respect to the inquiry and report to the Governor in Council by July 1, 1998.
